{
  "texts": [
    "Accuracy and F1 score for the fact-checking with context on the multilingual dataset.",
    "Accuracy English and F1 English are the scores for the case where the models are provided with English translation of the claims while the other scores are computed in the case where the models are provided with the original claims.",
    "differs over time we plot the accuracy of all four conditions (2 models x 2 context conditions) in Figure 5.",
    "The accuracy of all four conditions exhibits an upward trend over time.",
    "For the context condition, this improvement can likely be attributed to an increasing availability of relevant information on Google over recent years."
  ]
}